                        <p>Delivering reliable, high-speed internet connectivity to businesses and communities across Africa with cutting-edge infrastructure.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="service-highlight">
                        <div class="service-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">CCTV & Security Systems</h4>
                        <p>Advanced surveillance and security solutions protecting businesses, facilities, and communities with state-of-the-art technology.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="service-highlight">
                        <div class="service-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Renewable Energy Solutions</h4>
                        <p>Sustainable solar and renewable energy systems enabling businesses to reduce costs and environmental impact simultaneously.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="service-highlight">
                        <div class="service-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-code-slash"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Software Development</h4>
                        <p>Custom software solutions tailored to unique business needs, from web applications to enterprise systems and mobile platforms.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                    <div class="service-highlight">
                        <div class="service-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-diagram-3"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Network Infrastructure</h4>
                        <p>Robust network design and implementation providing secure, scalable infrastructure for modern organizations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
                    <div class="service-highlight">
                        <div class="service-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-chat-dots"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">IT Consulting & Procurement</h4>
                        <p>Strategic technology advisory and procurement services helping organizations navigate digital transformation effectively.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Company Strengths Section -->
    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center display-5 fw-bold mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">Our Competitive Strengths</h2>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="strength-card">
                        <div class="strength-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Proven Expertise</h4>
                        <p>With over a decade of experience, our deep industry knowledge ensures successful project delivery every time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="strength-card">
                        <div class="strength-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-gear-fill"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Cutting-Edge Technology</h4>
                        <p>Leveraging the latest technologies and best practices to deliver innovative solutions that drive real business value.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="strength-card">
                        <div class="strength-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Expert Team</h4>
                        <p>A diverse team of talented professionals committed to excellence, innovation, and client success.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="strength-card">
                        <div class="strength-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Quality Assurance</h4>
                        <p>Rigorous quality processes ensuring every deliverable meets the highest standards of excellence.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                    <div class="strength-card">
                        <div class="strength-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-globe"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">African Focus</h4>
                        <p>Deep understanding of African markets, challenges, and opportunities enables tailored solutions for regional success.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
                    <div class="strength-card">
                        <div class="strength-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-handshake"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Partnership Approach</h4>
                        <p>We don't just deliver projects – we become true partners invested in your long-term success and growth.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Quote Section -->
    <section class="quote-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                    <div class="quote-card" data-aos="zoom-in">
                        <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
                        <h3 class="fw-light mb-4">At Phoenix Innovative Technologies, we believe technology has the power to transform lives and unlock potential across Africa. Our mission is to be the catalyst for that transformation, delivering solutions that empower businesses, communities, and individuals to achieve their dreams in an increasingly digital world.</h3>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-0">Dr. Adewale Ogunleye</h5>
                            <p class="text-muted">Founder & CEO</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h2 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4" data-aos="fade-up">Ready to Partner With Us?</h2>
                    <p class="lead mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">Let's transform your business and drive digital innovation together</p>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light btn-lg px-5 py-3">Get In Touch</a>
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-5 py-3">View Our Services</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('../partials/footer'); %>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/animations.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/transitions.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init({
            duration: 1000,
            once: true,
            offset: 100
        });

        // Counter animation
        function animateCounter(element, target) {
            let current = 0;
            const increment = target / 50;
            const timer = setInterval(() => {
                current += increment;
                if (current >= target) {
                    element.textContent = target;
                    clearInterval(timer);
                } else {
                    element.textContent = Math.floor(current);
                }
            }, 20);
        }

        const counters = document.querySelectorAll('.counter-value');
        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                    const target = parseFloat(entry.target.dataset.target);
                    animateCounter(entry.target, target);
                    observer.unobserve(entry.target);
                }
            });
        }, { threshold: 0.5 });

        counters.forEach(counter => observer.observe(counter));
    </script>
</body>
</html>